                <mj-text mj-class="paddit">Hello {firstName},</mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit">Welcome to our latest newsletter from Rapid! Dive into this edition to discover the latest updates, insightful articles, and innovative features shaping the future of software solutions. Stay connected with us as we continue to redefine possibilities in the digital landscape for the public sector.</mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit"><a href="https://www.camden.gov.uk/" target="_blank" title="Camden Council">Camden Council</a>, a London Local Authority, partnered with Rapid to develop a bespoke billing solution for its district heating networks. The solution, introduced in 2023, automates the energy billing and compliance process, integrates with the council’s housing database, and allows residents to view their meter usage data online. It streamlines the calculation of energy charges, generates personalized bills, and ensures compliance with the Heat Network Regulations. The solution has increased process efficiency, reduced errors, and improved customer satisfaction. It has also saved significant staff time and lowered standing charges for residents. This innovative solution has potential benefits for the wider social housing sector and more detail of the case study can be viewed on <a href="https://rapid-is.co.uk/case-studies/camden-council-improving-energy-calculations-and-compliance/" title="Camden Council: Improving energy calculations and compliance" target="_blank">our website</a>.</mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit">The Billing System has been shortlisted for the Digital Award held by <a href="https://www.theade.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="The Association for Decentralised Energy">the Association for Decentralised Energy (ADE)</a> being held in May in Westminster. It has also been shortlisted for Collaboration of the year as part of the Innovation and Research Awards being held in Manchester at the end of June.</mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit">We are incredibly proud, in partnership with Camden, to have been shortlisted for both awards. We are aware that the entries are very competitive.</mj-text>
                <mj-text mj-class="paddit">If you would like to learn more about the Billing Solution after reading the case study above, please do get in <a href="https://rapid-is.co.uk/contact/" title="Contact Rapid" target="_blank">contact</a>.</mj-text>
            </mj-column>
